{
  "stem": "24212.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, we were assigned to these two factories, and I was assigned to a machine which was, oh, about five meters long.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it had big spools-- what is that, about a foot?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And behind my machine-- oh, the-- this five-meter long machine had I don't know how many dozens of these big spools-- and they were fed from behind my machine from big bins.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were strips of cotton about-- what is that, four inches, five inches wide-- and half an inch thick.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they went through a-- a row of needles, and evidently those needles divided that-- that strip of cotton.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so then, by the time I saw the cotton, it came in a very thick thread, I would say, about like my finger.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the spools were winding it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had on top of these spools-- there were two rows of spools-- and then there was a-- an iron rod.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the iron rod I could stop or start.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All the-- all the spools started by that rod.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And of course, whenever the supervisor went to the john or looked out the window, we would stop this thing, [LAUGHS] just watching the supervisor-- German supervisor, a civilian.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when she start returning, we started the machine, to slow down the production, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or we learned very well how to, just with a touch of a finger, we could break the thread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course the moment the thread was broken, we had to stop the machine and reattach the thread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That took a little time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was the little thing we could do, you know, for the Allies, to-- to slow down the War Production.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But multiply that with the hundreds of thousands of prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
